caption.title: Key meteorological forcing data and variations of mosquito populations in scenario S0).
caption.p:
(a) Daily precipitation; (b) Mean daily air temperature; (c) Population dynamics of mosquitoes in three aquatic phases (egg E, larval L, and pupal P) in the S-ELPAs model; and (d) Population dynamics of mosquitoes in three adult stages (host seeking A
h , resting A
r , and oviposition site searching A
o ) in the S-ELPAs model. A
total represents the sum of adult mosquitoes in all phases.
